{"word":"G2617 - καταισχύνω - kataischýnō - kat-ahee-skhoo'-no - Confound","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταισχύνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kataischýnō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-ahee-skhoo'-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Confound</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெட்கப்படு, வேதனைப்படு"},{"paragraph":"1. to dishonor, disgrace"},{"paragraph":"2. to put to shame, make ashamed"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G153 - αἰσχύνομαι - aischýnomai - ahee-skhoo'-nom-ahee/153\">G153</a>; to <i>shame down</i>, that is, <i>disgrace</i> or (by implication) <i>put to the blush:</i> - confound, dishonour, (be a-, make a-) shame (-d).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G150/150\">G150</a>, <a href=\"#/G151/151\">G151</a>, <a href=\"#/G152/152\">G152</a>, <a href=\"#/G153/153\">G153</a>, <a href=\"#/G1870/1870\">G1870</a>, <a href=\"#/G2617/2617\">G2617</a>"}]}